data.description: Luxury Living located near shopping, restaurants, and more at Meridian Buckhead. This high rise unit boasts unobstructed views of Atlanta, covered balcony, updated features and hardwood floors throughout. It also offers an open floor plan from living area to kitchen, in unit laundry and oversized Primary Bedroom with a large bathroom. Community features include 24hr concierge service, roof top pool with spectacular views, sports lounge, State of the art theatre room, and in-house salon just to name a few! You don't want to miss out on this luxury, call today for your private showing.
